- cs.SI (Social and Information Networks): The paper discusses the use of randomized gossip in decentralized optimization, which is a common technique used in social and information networks. 
- cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture): The paper proposes an algorithm for directed networks, which falls under the scope of networking and internet architecture. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control): The paper discusses the implementation and performance of the proposed algorithm, which falls under the scope of systems and control.
